WEBVTT

09:55.420 --> 09:58.050 line:80%
It has been said
that the Marquis of Wu'an fell in battle,

09:58.050 --> 10:00.410 line:80%
yet his body
hasn't been found to this day.

10:00.710 --> 10:02.500 line:80%
I have kept the news undisclosed

10:02.500 --> 10:04.670 line:80%
to mislead the enemy.
